HEADWORD: Universal donor
<hw>U`ni*ver"sal do"nor</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>a
person belonging to the O blood group (of the ABO classification), who
can safely donate blood to anyone.</def>⟦br⟧
